A depraved criminal reportedly beat and strangled his 90-year-old grandmother one day after he was released from prison.

Darel Agerton, 38, of Joliet, Illinois, was taken into custody on Wednesday afternoon for the November 30 death of Veronica Schick, whose unconscious body was found on the floor of her home.

Agerton was staying at Schick's home at the time of his grandmother's death.

